Interface NodeFactoryUtil


  • @Requireable(value="NodeFactoryUtil")
public interface NodeFactoryUtil
    Node factory utility interface.

    An instance of the Sitevision class implementing this interface can be obtained via Utils.getNodeFactoryUtil(). See Utils for how to obtain an instance of the Utils interface.
